{"tid":1481150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"反送中運動上咗 韓國時報 同 韓國Sunday 頭版","createTime":"2019-08-17T15:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T01:52:34.000Z","uid":288559,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"055018d9934ba7046b9d9836789cfde0d854d9ac","tid":1481150,"uid":288559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:01:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">今日我經過 Seoul Metro <br />\n諗住望下報紙攤檔有冇咩特別新聞關於我哋<br />\n然後再望一望就見到有黃色頭盔同美國國旗嘅相喺頭版</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原來我哋上咗韓國頭版呀！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r42wdq4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr42wdq4.jpg&h=88278579&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ay2DCSO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fay2DCSO.jpg&h=29617f4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我唔識韓文所以唔知佢講緊啲咩<br />\n但大概都係關於反送中<br />\n如果有識韓文嘅手足<br />\n請幫手翻譯一下</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">然後再望一望左邊</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到⋯⋯<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fBTWpyk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfBTWpyk.jpg&h=b540b188&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EyncHj4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEyncHj4.jpg&h=e03705ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q8QBpys.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq8QBpys.jpg&h=dec80881&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c88bXTw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc88bXTw.jpg&h=c10d0124&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上頭版真係要多得咁多位手足嘅努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，我搭車搵路嘅時候，咁啱有位韓國人過嚟幫我手。然後仲問我係咪香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，然後就開始傾起反送中嘅嘢，仲有餐廳老闆都好關心。同埋亦都好支持我哋，知道點解我哋要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n所以其實全球各地都好關心我哋㗎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"21c8224c2efdac78836bde9b29013f182bbfc16f","tid":1481150,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71efc16cffb15a9956e81e576317c43972582e9","tid":1481150,"uid":219564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:02:50.000Z","msg":"聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1985db84b18f188492b0423fd3f279c2d3586451","tid":1481150,"uid":138609,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:03:29.000Z","msg":"韓國人既民主都係流血爭取返黎<br />\n佢地經歷過獨裁政權既打壓<br />\n更加明白香港人做緊既野"},{"pid":"3bb5a3eeee5f8c6262cbb66479277757e73b9398","tid":1481150,"uid":301929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:03:38.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"dd5da0a1d2cceec6f76f1d759b1a204877277024","tid":1481150,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:03:45.000Z","msg":"逆權先驅we connect <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33dd42311a84267f8eb274f489865cdb98c228d","tid":1481150,"uid":288559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:04:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-lar